snippet.title: HALLELUJAH ALL MY LIFE | ANGEL SERAPHS | CHRISTIAN WORSHIP SONG | 4K
snippet.description:
Hallelujah All My Life - a worship song to the Lord for His sacrifice on the cross and for His everlasting faithfulness to lead His people in paths of righteousness. All our lives, let us sing Hallelujah to the King! 

Listen on the following platforms: 
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/1MLZZFHoDlk31P2jpgeX1P 
iTunes: http://itunes.apple.com/album/id1622318946?ls=1&app=itunes
Apple Music: http://itunes.apple.com/album/id/1622318946

Lyrics: 
Verse 1
You gave direction when there was no map in my life 
Darkness turned bright when you shined your light
You broke the walls of sin through your blood and your might  
Dead bones come to life when touched by your fire

Pre-Chorus
There is power in your name 
There is freedom in your name 

Chorus
You fight the battles that I cannot see 
Took all my shame and gave me victory 
I am grateful for your death on that tree
Glory Glory to the Son who sets me free 

Verse 2 
You made a way when there seemed to be no way 
Crooked paths made straight when you are here to stay 
Colours formed in me when all I saw was grey 
Everything I need Lord, is found in Your grace 

Bridge 
Hallelujah to the King who reigns 
Hallelujah to the One who saves 
Hallelujah to the Son He gave 
Hallelujah all my life I‚Äôll say

Thisai theriya Yoseppai thedi
Deva thoothan vilambinarae
Mariyaalai serthu kolla iyyathae

Visuvasithu varuvaaya
